    dc:description "Figs.18–21.Aedeagus (a – dorsal view; b – lateral view; c – ventral view). 18 – Mimastra sumatrensis Jacoby, 1884; 19 – M. jelineki sp. nov.; 20 – M. kremitovskyi sp. nov.; 21 – M. riedeli sp. nov. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
