    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5324984>
    dc:description "Figs. 30–32. Habitus. 30 – Mimastra jelineki sp. nov. (paratype, female, 8.60 mm); 31 – M. kremitovskyi sp. nov. (paratype, female, 8.45 mm); 32 – M. riedeli sp. nov. (paratype, male, 7.25 mm)." ;
